國立交通大學機構典藏：頻譜規劃配置與管理基礎研究---子計畫二：無線頻譜執照釋出的機制設計(I)



























































Please click here if you are not redirected within a few seconds.
Skip navigation
















目前位置：國立交通大學機構典藏
學術出版
研究計畫






















標題: 頻譜規劃配置與管理基礎研究---子計畫二：無線頻譜執照釋出的機制設計(I)Mechanism Design for Releasing Radio Spectrum Licenses(I)
作者: 梁高榮LIANG Gau-Rong國立交通大學工業工程與管理學系(所)
關鍵字: 無線頻譜執照;機制設計;私有財模式;公有財模式;Radio Spectrum License;Mechanism Design;Private Goods Model;PublicGoods Model
公開日期: 2008
摘要: 無線頻譜執照的釋出通常包括三個階段：執照的規格設計，執照釋出的機制設計，
及相關法令的設計。換言之，電信產業的專家們會先分析無線頻譜執照的性質，而設
計出其規格。接著賽局理論專家們會依給予的規格而設計出其執照釋出機制。在實作
出賽局規則後，律師再將賽局規則轉成相關的法令。
在此三年期的計畫裡，主要的研究目標是和其它的整合型子計畫合作設計出執照釋
出機制。本質上，執照規格可分成私有財模式或公有財模式兩大類；而私有財模式更
可細分為三種拍賣模式：私有價值模式，隸屬價值模式，與共同價值模式。從此角度
來看，第一年的主要研究方向是在改善台灣現有的多回合拍賣模式。這意味著用斂核
觀念取代傳統的核觀念來縮短拍賣時間。在第二年裡，其它的整合型子計畫會各別完
成私有財與公有財的執照規格設計。屆時研究目標會轉成實作私有財執照釋出的賽局
法則。在第三年裡，研究目標則是實作公有財執照的賽局法則。A release of radio spectrum licenses usually consists of three stages: the specification
design of licenses, the mechanism design of license release, and the design of related laws.
In other words, the experts of telecommunication industry analyze the properties of radio
spectrum licenses and design their specification. Then the experts of game theory design the
licenses release mechanism according to the given specification. After the implementation of
the game rules, the lawyers make the laws from the game rules.
In this three-year project, the main research goal is how to design the licenses release
mechanism with other cooperatively integrated projects. Essentially license specifications
can be classified into private goods model or public goods model; moreover, the private
goods model involves three auction models: private value model, affiliated value model, and
common value model. From this viewpoint, the major research effort is to improve the
current multi-round auction model used in Taiwan at the first year. It means to shorten the
long auctioning period using nucleolus concept instead of the traditional core concept. At the
second year, the private and the public goods license specification designs are going to be
finished separately from other integrated projects. Then the research goal is transformed into
implementing the game rules of license release with private goods properties. At the third
year, the research goal is to implement the game rules of public goods licenses.
官方說明文件#: NSC97-2219-E009-013
URI: http://hdl.handle.net/11536/102518https://www.grb.gov.tw/search/planDetail?id=1686962&docId=290836
顯示於類別：研究計畫




















